These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, poker, snooker, chess, backgammon, go
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy, azalea, tulip, orchid, lily, aconite
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing chess is the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing go is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Game           | chess | snooker | monopoly | poker | bridge | backgammon | go |
| Flower   | iris    | orchid   | tulip      | lily | azalea    | daisy    | aconite         |

