.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, nigerian, russian, spanish, indonesian, malaysian, brazilian
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, architect, librarian, pilot, lawyer, analyst, social-worker
 1. the lawyer is the spanish##1
 2. the malaysian is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the analyst is on the far right##1
 4. the nigerian is on the right of the architect##1
 5. the spanish is on the right of the pilot##1
 6. the malaysian is on the left of the brazilian##1
 7. the lawyer is in the middle##1
 8. the lawyer is on the right of the indonesian##1
 9. the social-worker is on the left of the russian##1
10. the spanish is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Nationality          | turkish | nigerian | indonesian | spanish | malaysian | brazilian | russian |
| Job   | architect      | librarian   | pilot   | lawyer      | dressmaker       | social-worker       | analyst     |

