.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, goat, chinchilla, dog, turtle, cat
House: tower, wooden, palace, victorian, art-deco, craftsman, colonial
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the colonial house##1
 3. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the tower house is the owner of the dog##1
 6. the palace house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 7. the wooden house is on the left of the palace house##1
 8. the wooden house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is the victorian house##1
10. the owner of the goat is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the victorian house is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Pet   | rabbit | dog     | goat  | turtle       | snake       | cat  | chinchilla   |
| House    | craftsman  | tower | colonial | victorian | wooden | palace | art-deco |

