.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, tea, juice, 7up, water, soy-milk
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, lily, iris, bellflower, aconite, amaryllis
 1. the person drinking 7up is the person who growspoppy##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person drinking tea is the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | water    | soy-milk     | juice     | tea      | cola | 7up      | fanta     |
| Flower   | iris | lily | aconite | bellflower | amaryllis | poppy | dahlia |

