.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, tea, almond-milk, sprite
The people use 7 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, snowmobile, boat, van, car, taxi
 1. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 3. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person driving the van is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage   | coffee | fanta | almond-milk     | soy-milk | sprite | tea | milk |
| Transport     | taxi   | snowmobile    | van | car     | skateboard         | boat     | roller        |

