 8. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
