The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, december, february, january, august, may, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to colone##1
 2. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |      4       |  5   |     6     |     7      |
| City   | colone | san-francisco | edinburgh   | rome | london | marseilles | berlin        |
| Birthday     | may | january | february | october         | december  | july    | august |

